author: paulb
msg: Packaging jclouds in the amazon node launcher bundle. We might want to consider doing this different by using the jclouds OSGi jars directly, but this is a pain as far as I know because the huge amount of dependencies. The included groovy scripts can be run from the command line to help when upgrading to a newer jclouds version.
